Package org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.song.filter

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SearchFilter<T>
    Represents a generic filter that evaluate a predicate against an instance of a given type.
    SongSearchFilter
    Represents a custom SearchFilter of a song.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SongSearchFilterImpl<V>
    Represents a basic implementation of SongSearchFilter that takes an object of a generic type which can be used for the evaluation of the filter through SearchFilter.check(Object).
    SongSearchFilters
    Contains all the filters that operate on Song.
    SongSearchFilters.Album
    SongSearchFilter that operates on Song.getAlbum().
    SongSearchFilters.Artist
    SongSearchFilter that operates on Song.getArtist().
    SongSearchFilters.Cover
    SongSearchFilter that operate on Song.getCover().
    SongSearchFilters.Genre
    SongSearchFilter that operate on Song.getGenre().
    SongSearchFilters.Lyrics
    SongSearchFilter that operate on Song.getLyrics().
    SongSearchFilters.Title
    SongSearchFilter that operates on Song.getTitle().
    SongSearchFilters.Year
    SongSearchFilter that operate on Song.getYear().
